text: Jeannette Rosita Young (born 1963) is an Australian politician, physician and medical administrator. She is the current governor of the state of Queensland since 2021. Young was the Chief Health Officer of Queensland Health from 2005 to 2021. ==Notes== ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Governors of Queensland Category:Politicians from Sydney Category:Australian medical doctors
